### POST /api/v1/admin/tariffs
### Descripción: Crear plan de tarifa. Requiere Admin/Support + X-Tenant-Id.
### Headers requeridos: Authorization: Bearer <token>, X-Tenant-Id: <guid>
### Códigos: 200 OK (TariffPlanDto) | 400 { "error", "code" }

# @name createTariff
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/admin/tariffs
Authorization: Bearer {{ACCESS_TOKEN}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{TENANT_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Standard",
  "currency": "USD",
  "baseFare": 5.00,
  "pricePerKm": 1.50,
  "pricePerMinute": 0.25,
  "minimumFare": 8.00,
  "priority": 100,
  "effectiveFromUtc": null,
  "effectiveUntilUtc": null
}

### Response esperado (200):
# {
#   "id", "tenantId", "name", "currency", "baseFare", "pricePerKm", "pricePerMinute", "minimumFare",
#   "isActive", "priority", "effectiveFromUtc", "effectiveUntilUtc", "createdAtUtc"
# }

### Response error (400):
# { "error": "string", "code": "string" }
